<h3>Product Details</h3>
<p>The Custom Jr. is an ultra-slim flatware organizer.  This unit was designed for flatware in narrow drawers.  You decide the width (up to 16&#8243;) and usable depth needed (up to 13&#8243;).  The Custom Jr. is unique in that it is meant to fill your drawer width, but not necessarily your drawer depth.  We&#8217;ll size the organizer&#8217;s depth based on your longest flatware utensil up to 13&#8243; in length.  You&#8217;ll also get the versatility of a classic, traditional slot-and-divider system.  Movable dividers allow micro-adjustability to make the most of your space.  Attached wood bottom is optional. This custom  organizer includes four hardwood wedges to lock it in place &#8212; no more  sliding organizer!</p>
<p>(Custom Mat not included with this insert.  It is <a href="/the-custom-jr/mat">available here</a>)</p>
